author: julianfoad
msg: Simplify the internal scan_addition() to return repository id instead of URL
and UUID, for both of its repository outputs.  Move that look-up up to the
semi-public wrapper svn_wc__db_scan_addition().  Simplify the other callers,
as they only wanted the repos id anyway.
(scan_addition): Replace URL/UUID output parameters with repos_id, twice.
(svn_wc__db_scan_addition): Convert to URL and UUID here.
(get_info_for_copy): Simplify: eliminate the reverse look-ups of repos id.
